title: Lombardi's Week 7 Watch List and Last-Second Fantasy Advice | GM Street (Ep. 326)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier react to the Broncos’ shellacking of the Cardinals on 'Thursday Night Football' (02:00) and name their favorite Week 7 matchups (10:30). Then Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly of 'The Dantasy Football Podcast' offer up some fantasy football advice for this weekend (29:45).
